## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="2c42d-103">辨別名稱的延伸的形式包含的物件 objectGUID 屬性的字串表示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c42d-103">The extended form of a distinguished name includes a string representation of the objectGUID property of an object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c42d-104">安全性主體物件，例如使用者、 群組及電腦，延伸的形式也包含 [objectSID] 屬性的字串表示。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c42d-104">For security principal objects such as users, groups, and computers, the extended form also includes a string representation of the objectSID property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="2c42d-105">如需 objectGUID 和 objectSID 屬性的詳細資訊，請參閱主題[物件 Guid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp)和[物件 Sid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp)在 MSDN Library 中[ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c42d-105">For more information about the objectGUID and objectSID properties, see the topics [Object-Guid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) and [Object-Sid](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_objectguid.asp) in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="2c42d-106">下列 C# 範例會示範如何以十六進位格式傳回辨別名稱的集合。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="2c42d-106">The following C# example shows how to return a collection of distinguished names in hexadecimal format.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.ExtendedDN = ExtendedDN.HexString;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```
